PlackX-Framework version 0.01
=============================

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  Plack
  Plack::Request
  Plack::Response

